    <node id="&quot;FEZZIWIG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Fezziwig is Ebenezer's former boss, known for his benevolence and jovial spirit."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fezziwig is a generous and kind-hearted employer whom Scrooge remembers from his past."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fezziwig is described as a generous individual who hosts a lively Christmas party, inspiring gratitude in his employees."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fezziwig is mentioned by one of the men in the market as someone who would attend Jacob's funeral if a lunch was provided. It's unclear whether he's a real person or a fictional character within this story."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-cb661c37436355ccec2769b1d0350c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b2f98bc7abb0c67d4c86055c7fd72218&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c248858d1b13ab7ee9ca13c1aeed6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1a4fbcf1ed86864b9bfd5e8dba4c683</data>
