    <node id="&quot;CHRISTMAS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Christmas is depicted as an important event for the Cratchit family, bringing them together for a joyful celebration despite their poverty."&lt;SEP&gt;"Christmas is portrayed as a time of charity, kindness, and open-heartedness, which Scrooge initially rejects."&lt;SEP&gt;"Christmas is portrayed as a time when Want is keenly felt, and Abundance rejoices, but Scrooge does not participate in its festivities."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-503f0bfa5453467c7c61d160a3540eca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-90d5764e301321c087f5a8f78b73a145&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dac41b3f9eeaf794f0147400b1718cd</data>
    </node>
