    <node id="&quot;MRS. CRATCHIT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob Cratchit's loving and caring wife, who manages their household and raises their children with kindness and warmth."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob Cratchit's wife who cares deeply for her family and works hard to provide for them."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob Cratchit's wife, who kisses little Bob and shares in his happiness."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob's wife who dresses in a twice-turned gown but bravely wears ribbons for Christmas."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is Bob's wife who has strong opinions about Mr. Scrooge and is concerned about their financial situation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is portrayed as a nervous but proud woman who prepares and serves a large Christmas pudding for her family."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mrs. Cratchit is the mother of the Cratchit family, focused on preparing a Christmas meal despite their financial struggles."</data>
