      <data key="d2">chunk-83ac129dc9b56f84c46760d153d68e93</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;BOY (SOLITARY CHILD)&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The boy, neglected by his friends, is left at the school during Christmas, evoking pity from Scrooge."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;FRED&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Fred is Scrooge's nephew who shows great warmth towards his uncle."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fred is Scrooge's nephew, known for his kindness and generosity, unlike some other members of the family."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fred is introduced as Scrooge's nephew who initiates a game of guessing the identity of his uncle."&lt;SEP&gt;"Fred, Scrooge's nephew, is mentioned as someone who still cares for Scrooge despite his miserly ways."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge's nephew is named Fred, and he is the primary source of joy and laughter in the gathering."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-19fcf3bed0b4df750efc07831690f550&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7637ff18c5ded77a68cce0a87883fad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bb21d58d36c6306fd8810ddd51c4a971&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-773d0df1dd25c356f7b771d780583e09</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;SCROOGE’S NEPHEW&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Scrooge's nephew participates in the guessing game and reveals that his uncle is Scrooge."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-e7637ff18c5ded77a68cce0a87883fad</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;TIM CRATCHIT (TINY TIM)&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Tim Cratchit, also known as Tiny Tim, is the youngest son of Bob Cratchit and a cripple with a heart full of love and gratitude."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;PRESENT&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Present is one of the three realms visited by Scrooge through the second spirit."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-cb661c37436355ccec2769b1d0350c5f</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;JANUARY 6TH PROTESTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The January 6th protests at the U.S. Capitol resulted in violence, five deaths, and led to Trump's impeachment by the House of Representatives."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-359187e7571bda4b0b08b2e0b6581e52</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE HOUSE-FRONTS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"GEO"</data>
