      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;EBENEZER (YOUNG)&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Ebenezer in his younger form, working as an apprentice under Fezziwig."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-c6c248858d1b13ab7ee9ca13c1aeed6b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE POOR MINER&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The Poor Miner is an event where Scrooge sees a miner struggling with his heavy load, reflecting on his past charity towards the man."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-bb21d58d36c6306fd8810ddd51c4a971</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. SCROOGE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Mr. Scrooge is introduced as a character who has given merriment to others, with suggestions of being ungrateful if they did not drink his health."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mr. Scrooge is portrayed as an odious, stingy man who is the source of discontent among his family members during Christmas Day."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-e7637ff18c5ded77a68cce0a87883fad&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19d72c57ae3408758b18d2568e86dc6b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;MR. FEZZIWIG&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
