      <data key="d2">chunk-8590d9263cd2cd4fa583c432fc54e6c3</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;DICK WILKINS&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Dick Wilkins is Ebenezer Scrooge's former self and fellow-'prentice, who is very much attached to him."&lt;SEP&gt;"Dick Wilkins is Ebenezer's fellow-apprentice, who is very attached to Ebenezer."&lt;SEP&gt;"Dick Wilkins was Scrooge's fellow apprentice in the past, with whom he had a falling out over Belle."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-8bc1edd983869352d14cf0886a9175a7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6c248858d1b13ab7ee9ca13c1aeed6b</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;EBENEZER SCROOGE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Ebenezer Scrooge is described as a young man working with Dick Wilkins under Fezziwig."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ebenezer Scrooge is portrayed as a miserly and solitary individual, with no warmth towards others. He is the main character of this text."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ebenezer Scrooge is the main character who experiences a mysterious event on Christmas Eve."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ebenezer Scrooge is the protagonist of A Christmas Carol, known for his miserliness, selfishness, and lack of empathy towards others."&lt;SEP&gt;"Scrooge is portrayed as a miserly and selfish man who dislikes Christmas and is initially cold towards his nephew."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-9e3921da66da5d761ab73cd849af6c43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c7b10789a9cb0af6c553730b29bd9034&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74e2466de2f67fd710ef2f20c0a8d9e0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dac41b3f9eeaf794f0147400b1718cd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bc1edd983869352d14cf0886a9175a7</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;IGNORANCE&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"CATEGORY"</data>
      <data key="d1">"Ignorance is described as a boy who clings to the Spirit, appealing from their fathers. He represents the negative influence of ignorance on humanity."&lt;SEP&gt;"Ignorance is portrayed as a boy clinging to the Spirit, appealing for help and carrying a prophecy of doom on his brow."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-02baee20cc9463dbe08170a8e1043e32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e7637ff18c5ded77a68cce0a87883fad</data>
    </node>
