      <data key="d1">"The Spirit of Christmas Yet to Come is an entity that shows Scrooge visions of the future, specifically his own death and burial place."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-91572b3cd42786ba4cb2f180ca25cbf4</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;GREAT BRITAIN&quot;">
