    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE FIRST WOMAN&quot;">
      <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
      <data key="d1">"The First Woman is described as bold and defiant, engaging in scavenging with others despite knowing it's wrong."&lt;SEP&gt;"The First Woman is one of the women present with Old Joe, scavenging items from the deceased man's house. She expresses disregard for his possessions and shows no remorse."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-60fc063c79fc0d4acc91a57e79de04dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1f29eeadc1d8ab46dc8a0bbd3c56b64</data>
    </node>
    <node id="&quot;THE SHORTEST STREETS&quot;">
